column5: Here's a shot of a chair lift at the top of a hill, the snow is over the chair!
They have had 15' of snow and 44" of rain fall in Cordova since November 1st. In Valdez they have had almost 26 1/2' of snow fall in the same time period.   Some Valdez Pics  And Some Cordova Pics
Guess we know were winter has been stuck the last 2 months!
